---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Smart Home Buying Guides (2026)" description="Researched buying guides for smart thermostats, locks, cameras, lighting, and smart plugs. Honest comparisons built for homeowners and renters.">

  <section class="bg-gray-50 border-b border-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-green-700 uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Category Guide</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Smart Home Devices</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
        Buying guides for smart thermostats, locks, cameras, lighting, and smart plugs.
        We focus on devices that work reliably in real homes — not just in demo conditions.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">

    <!-- Thermostats -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
        <span class="text-2xl">🌡️</span>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Smart Thermostats</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6 ml-10">Save 10–15% on heating and cooling — the easiest smart home upgrade with a clear payback period.</p>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <a href="/smart-home/best-smart-thermostat-no-c-wire" class="group block border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-5 hover:border-green-200 hover:shadow-sm transition-all">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1 group-hover:text-green-700 transition-colors text-sm">Best Smart Thermostats Without C-Wire →</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">For older homes where adding a C-wire would mean calling an electrician. 3 picks that work without it — from $129.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/smart-home/best-smart-thermostat-multiple-zones" class="group block border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-5 hover:border-green-200 hover:shadow-sm transition-all">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1 group-hover:text-green-700 transition-colors text-sm">Best Smart Thermostats for Multiple Zones →</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">Sensor-based zoning vs true HVAC zoning. The ecobee and Honeywell T9 compared for multi-room temperature control.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Smart Locks -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
        <span class="text-2xl">🔐</span>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Smart Locks</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6 ml-10">Keyless entry, remote access, and guest codes — for homeowners and renters alike.</p>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <a href="/smart-home/best-smart-lock-for-renters" class="group block border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-5 hover:border-green-200 hover:shadow-sm transition-all">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1 group-hover:text-green-700 transition-colors text-sm">Best Smart Locks for Renters →</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">Options that don't require landlord permission or permanent modifications. Our top pick installs in 5 minutes and leaves no exterior trace.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Cameras -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
        <span class="text-2xl">📷</span>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Security Cameras</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6 ml-10">Monitor your home from anywhere — no drilling, no subscriptions required.</p>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <a href="/smart-home/best-smart-camera-for-apartments" class="group block border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-5 hover:border-green-200 hover:shadow-sm transition-all">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1 group-hover:text-green-700 transition-colors text-sm">Best Smart Security Cameras for Apartments →</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">Shelf-mounted, no drilling required, free local storage. Wyze, Eufy, and Arlo compared from $36 to $100.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Lighting -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
        <span class="text-2xl">💡</span>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Smart Lighting</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6 ml-10">Automate your lights without rewiring — screw-in bulbs compared across all ecosystems.</p>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <a href="/smart-home/best-smart-lighting-for-apartments" class="group block border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-5 hover:border-green-200 hover:shadow-sm transition-all">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1 group-hover:text-green-700 transition-colors text-sm">Best Smart Lighting for Apartments →</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">4 bulb systems from $12 to $50 per bulb. All portable, no wiring, no landlord permission. Philips Hue, Kasa, Govee, and Nanoleaf.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Smart Plugs -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
        <span class="text-2xl">🔌</span>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Smart Plugs</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6 ml-10">Control any outlet from your phone — indoor and outdoor options for automation and energy monitoring.</p>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <a href="/smart-home/best-outdoor-smart-plugs" class="group block border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-5 hover:border-green-200 hover:shadow-sm transition-all">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1 group-hover:text-green-700 transition-colors text-sm">Best Outdoor Smart Plugs →</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">Weather-rated plugs for holiday lights, landscape lighting, and patio devices. Kasa, Meross, and Amazon compared.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Ecosystems -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
        <span class="text-2xl">🏡</span>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Ecosystems & Comparisons</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6 ml-10">Which platform should you build around? Alexa, Google Home, and Apple HomeKit compared for real-world use.</p>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <a href="/smart-home/google-home-vs-alexa" class="group block border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-5 hover:border-green-200 hover:shadow-sm transition-all">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1 group-hover:text-green-700 transition-colors text-sm">Google Home vs Alexa: Which Wins? →</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">Device support, automation quality, voice accuracy, and privacy compared. Our verdict: it depends on your existing device ecosystem.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- For Renters -->
    <section class="mb-4">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
        <span class="text-2xl">🏢</span>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">For Renters</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6 ml-10">No drilling, no permanent modifications, no landlord permission needed. Smart home upgrades that move with you.</p>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <a href="/smart-home/best-smart-home-devices-for-renters" class="group block border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-5 hover:border-green-200 hover:shadow-sm transition-all">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1 group-hover:text-green-700 transition-colors text-sm">Best Smart Home Devices for Renters →</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">The complete renter-friendly smart home — one top pick per category, everything fully portable. Build it in stages or all at once.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/smart-home/best-smart-home-starter-kit-under-500" class="group block border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-5 hover:border-green-200 hover:shadow-sm transition-all">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1 group-hover:text-green-700 transition-colors text-sm">Best Smart Home Starter Kit Under $500 →</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">Three curated starter kits by budget — $150, $300, and $500. Covers what to buy first and what to add later.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

  </div>
</Layout>
